        { "type": "text", "content": "[500] ", "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": 500, "fontStyle": "italic" } } },
        { "type": "text", "content": "[700] ", "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": 700, "fontStyle": "italic" } } },
        { "type": "text", "content": "[900]",  "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": 900, "fontStyle": "italic" } } }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "content": "Scripts & Mixed-Family Composition"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "content": "Type systems that serve international audiences must switch families mid-paragraph without disrupting baseline rhythm or line height. The examples below show style-level family overrides and inline family runs in a single composition."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "content": "",
      "children": [
        { "type": "text", "content": "Base Arimo 12pt, then " },
        { "type": "text", "content": "Courier Prime 11pt", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Courier Prime", "fontSize": 11 } } },
        { "type": "text", "content": ", then " },
        { "type": "text", "content": "Arimo Bold 15pt", "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": "bold", "fontSize": 15 } } },
        { "type": "text", "content": ", then " },
        { "type": "text", "content": "Arimo Italic 12pt", "properties": { "style": { "fontStyle": "italic" } } },
        { "type": "text", "content": "." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "mono",
      "content": "const total = subtotal + tax - discount; // style-level monospace family override"
    },
    {
      "type": "cjk",
      "content": "日本語サンプル: フォントファミリーを要素単位で切り替えても、改行と計測が安定することを確認します。"
    },
    {
      "type": "arabic",
      "content": "مثال عربي: هذا السطر يختبر استخدام عائلة خط مختلفة مع حجم مختلف داخل نفس المستند."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "content": "",
      "children": [
        { "type": "text", "content": "Mixed-script inline: " },
        { "type": "text", "content": "日本語", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Noto Sans JP", "fontSize": 13 } } },
        { "type": "text", "content": " + " },
        { "type": "text", "content": "العربية", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Noto Sans Arabic", "fontSize": 13 } } },
        { "type": "text", "content": " + " },
        { "type": "text", "content": "Courier", "properties": { "style": { "fontFamily": "Courier Prime", "fontSize": 11, "fontWeight": "bold" } } },
        { "type": "text", "content": " in one unbroken paragraph." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "content": "Cross-Family Weight Matching — Noto Sans"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "content": "Noto Sans is a static-instance family. Weight resolution falls back to nearest-match rather than variable interpolation, making it a useful contrast with Arimo's continuous axis."
    },
    {
      "type": "weightLineNoto",
      "content": "Noto Sans requested 200 → nearest static match (non-variable)",
      "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": 200 } }
    },
    {
      "type": "weightLineNoto",
      "content": "Noto Sans requested 500 → nearest static match boundary",
      "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": 500 } }
    },
    {
      "type": "weightLineNoto",
      "content": "Noto Sans requested 800 → nearest static match (non-variable)",
      "properties": { "style": { "fontWeight": 800 } }
    }
